@startuml brainana_Nextflow_Workflow_Sequence

!theme plain
skinparam sequenceMessageAlign center
skinparam responseMessageBelowArrow true

actor User
participant "Discovery Script" as Discovery
participant "Nextflow Pipeline" as Nextflow
participant "Step Functions" as Steps
participant "Processing Operations" as Ops
participant "Quality Control" as QC

User -> Discovery: ./run_nextflow.sh run main.nf --bids_dir /data --output_dir /output
activate Discovery

Discovery -> Discovery: Run BIDS discovery
Discovery -> Steps: discover_bids_dataset
activate Steps
Steps --> Discovery: anatomical_jobs, functional_jobs
deactivate Steps
Discovery -> Discovery: Save JSON files (anatomical_jobs.json, functional_jobs.json)
Discovery --> Discovery: Discovery complete
deactivate Discovery

User -> Nextflow: Nextflow starts (after discovery)
activate Nextflow

Nextflow -> Nextflow: Load configuration
Nextflow -> Nextflow: Read job JSON files

note over Nextflow: **PHASE 1: ANATOMICAL PROCESSING**\nAll anatomical steps run in parallel

par For each anatomical job (parallel)
    Nextflow -> Nextflow: T1W_SYNTHESIS (if multiple runs)
    Nextflow -> Nextflow: ANAT_REORIENT
    Nextflow -> Steps: anat_reorient
    activate Steps
    Steps -> Ops: reorient_image
    activate Ops
    Ops --> Steps: reoriented_file
    deactivate Ops
    Steps --> Nextflow: anat_reoriented
    deactivate Steps
    
    Nextflow -> Nextflow: ANAT_CONFORM
    Nextflow -> Steps: anat_conform
    activate Steps
    Steps -> Ops: conform_image
    activate Ops
    Ops --> Steps: conformed_file
    deactivate Ops
    Steps --> Nextflow: anat_conformed
    deactivate Steps
    
    Nextflow -> Nextflow: ANAT_BIAS_CORRECTION
    Nextflow -> Steps: anat_bias_correction
    activate Steps
    Steps -> Ops: bias_correction
    activate Ops
    Ops --> Steps: bias_corrected_file
    deactivate Ops
    Steps --> Nextflow: anat_bias_corrected
    deactivate Steps
    
    Nextflow [#0066CC]-> QC: create_bias_correction_qc
    activate QC
    QC -[#0066CC]-> Nextflow: anat_bias_qc_snapshot
    deactivate QC
    
    Nextflow -> Nextflow: ANAT_SKULLSTRIPPING (GPU)
    Nextflow -> Steps: anat_skullstripping
    activate Steps
    Steps -> Ops: skullstripping
    activate Ops
    Ops --> Steps: brain_mask
    deactivate Ops
    Steps --> Nextflow: anat_skullstripped
    deactivate Steps
    
    Nextflow [#0066CC]-> QC: create_skullstripping_qc
    activate QC
    QC -[#0066CC]-> Nextflow: anat_skull_qc_snapshot
    deactivate QC
    
    Nextflow -> Nextflow: ANAT_REGISTRATION
    Nextflow -> Steps: anat_registration
    activate Steps
    Steps -> Ops: ants_register
    activate Ops
    Ops --> Steps: registered_file
    deactivate Ops
    Steps --> Nextflow: anat_registered
    deactivate Steps
    
    Nextflow [#0066CC]-> QC: create_registration_qc
    activate QC
    QC -[#0066CC]-> Nextflow: anat_reg_qc_snapshot
    deactivate QC
end

note over Nextflow: **PHASE 2: FUNCTIONAL PROCESSING**\nAll functional steps run in parallel (after anatomical dependencies)

par For each functional job (parallel)
    Nextflow -> Nextflow: FUNC_REORIENT
    Nextflow -> Steps: func_reorient
    activate Steps
    Steps -> Ops: reorient_and_tmean
    activate Ops
    Ops --> Steps: reoriented_file, tmean_file
    deactivate Ops
    Steps --> Nextflow: func_reoriented
    deactivate Steps
    
    Nextflow -> Nextflow: FUNC_SLICE_TIMING
    Nextflow -> Steps: func_slice_timing_correction
    activate Steps
    Steps -> Ops: slice_timing_correction
    activate Ops
    Ops --> Steps: slice_timed_file
    deactivate Ops
    Steps --> Nextflow: func_slice_timed
    deactivate Steps
    
    Nextflow -> Nextflow: FUNC_MOTION_CORRECTION
    Nextflow -> Steps: func_motion_correction
    activate Steps
    Steps -> Ops: motion_correction
    activate Ops
    Ops --> Steps: motion_corrected_file
    deactivate Ops
    Steps --> Nextflow: func_motion_corrected
    deactivate Steps
    
    Nextflow [#0066CC]-> QC: create_motion_correction_qc
    activate QC
    QC -[#0066CC]-> Nextflow: motion_qc_snapshot
    deactivate QC
    
    Nextflow -> Nextflow: FUNC_DESPIKE
    Nextflow -> Steps: func_despike
    activate Steps
    Steps -> Ops: despike
    activate Ops
    Ops --> Steps: despiked_file
    deactivate Ops
    Steps --> Nextflow: func_despiked
    deactivate Steps
    
    Nextflow -> Nextflow: FUNC_BIAS_CORRECTION (on tmean)
    Nextflow -> Steps: func_bias_correction
    activate Steps
    Steps -> Ops: bias_correction
    activate Ops
    Ops --> Steps: bias_corrected_tmean
    deactivate Ops
    Steps --> Nextflow: func_bias_corrected
    deactivate Steps
    
    Nextflow -> Nextflow: FUNC_CONFORM (tmean)
    Nextflow -> Steps: func_conform
    activate Steps
    Steps -> Ops: conform_image
    activate Ops
    Ops --> Steps: conformed_tmean
    deactivate Ops
    Steps --> Nextflow: func_conformed
    deactivate Steps
    
    Nextflow -> Nextflow: FUNC_SKULLSTRIPPING (on tmean, GPU)
    Nextflow -> Steps: func_skullstripping
    activate Steps
    Steps -> Ops: skullstripping
    activate Ops
    Ops --> Steps: func_brain_mask
    deactivate Ops
    Steps --> Nextflow: func_skullstripped
    deactivate Steps
    
    Nextflow [#0066CC]-> QC: create_skullstripping_qc
    activate QC
    QC -[#0066CC]-> Nextflow: func_skull_qc_snapshot
    deactivate QC
    
    Nextflow -> Nextflow: FUNC_REGISTRATION (tmean to target)
    Nextflow -> Steps: func_registration
    activate Steps
    Steps -> Ops: ants_register
    activate Ops
    Ops --> Steps: registered_tmean
    deactivate Ops
    Steps --> Nextflow: func_registered
    deactivate Steps
    
    Nextflow -> Nextflow: FUNC_APPLY_TRANSFORMS (to full 4D BOLD)
    Nextflow -> Steps: func_apply_transforms
    activate Steps
    Steps -> Ops: ants_apply_transforms
    activate Ops
    Ops --> Steps: final_func_file
    deactivate Ops
    Steps --> Nextflow: func_final
    deactivate Steps
    
    Nextflow [#0066CC]-> QC: create_registration_qc
    activate QC
    QC -[#0066CC]-> Nextflow: func_reg_qc_snapshot
    deactivate QC
end

note over Nextflow: **PHASE 3: QC REPORT GENERATION**

Nextflow [#0066CC]-> Nextflow: QC_ANATOMICAL
Nextflow [#0066CC]-> Nextflow: QC_FUNCTIONAL
Nextflow [#0066CC]-> QC: generate_qc_report
activate QC
QC -[#0066CC]-> Nextflow: qc_report
deactivate QC

Nextflow --> User: Processing complete
deactivate Nextflow

@enduml
